AstrOsAnimationCommands
=======================

Pure, native-testable command parsing for the animation scripting system.
Parses pipe-delimited command template strings into typed command objects
(SerialCommand, I2cCommand, GpioCommand, MaestroCommand) used by both
AnimationController and the hardware Modules.

Purity rule
-----------

This library is unit-tested on the native host under [env:test], so it
must not include any of:

    freertos/*, esp_*, driver/*, nvs_*, sdmmc_*, esp_vfs*, esp_now*, esp_wifi*

Enforced by the CI purity guard in .github/workflows/pr-validation.yml.

Error-channel convention
------------------------

Command constructors set safe defaults (-1, empty string) when parsing
fails. No logging — the MIXED-layer caller (AnimationController, Modules)
can inspect fields and log at the boundary if needed.
